LBXnYW6yX_Q" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>该控制器与一些名为 Beta Zwift Play Game Experience 的全新软件一同发布。一种名为 Repack Rush 的游戏模式作为一种教程存在，教新用户如何充分利用他们的控制器，并在不久的将来推出更多游戏。还将举办更多的多人锦标赛，例如在中央公园的虚拟娱乐场所举行的<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/zwift-esports-cycling-championship-wahoo-kickr-153307855.html">一年一度的 UCI 自行车电子竞技世界锦标赛</a>。</p><p> Zwift Play 控制器从今天开始在美国和欧洲上市。这些控制器最初以 100 美元的折扣价出售，但在初始 Beta 测试阶段完成后最高可提高 150 美元。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/zwift-launches-dedicated-game-controllers-for-its-bike-based-fitness-platform-150046881.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/zwift-launches-dedicated-game-controllers-for-its-bike-based-fitness-platform-150046881.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4a088d95-d026-41f2-a62b-f3de0bf918de</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 14 Jun 2023 15:00:46 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686750465</ingested><modified> 2023-06-14T13:47:48+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/e60dd7a0-0a12-11ee-bfdd-2fd31ae23776" width="3840"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-up