-other-canned-hbo-shows-are-now-streaming-on-roku-for-free-183106349.html">在 Roku 和 Tubi 之类的网站上。</a></ins></p><p>您将能够通过 Freevee 应用程序、Fire TV 和 Prime Video 访问所有这些频道（您无需订阅 Amazon Prime 即可观看）。今年早些时候，<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/amazon/">亚马逊</a></ins>表示将制作 100 多部 Prime Video 节目和电影<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-is-making-over-100-prime-video-originals-available-for-free-160032958.html">免费提供</a></ins>通过 Freevee 的渠道。</p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/amazons-freevee-is-adding-free-mgm-and-warner-bros-discovery-channels-144339161.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/amazons-freevee-is-adding-free-mgm-and-warner-bros-discovery-channels-144339161.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 8964c0b4-7e55-41ac-9f53-453ab85a9dd0</guid><dc:creator>克里斯霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 14 Jun 2023 14:43:39 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686753531</ingested><modified> 2023-06-14T14:38:54+00:00</modified><category><![CDATA[Professional Services]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="781" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/7953fcd0-0ac0-11ee-9bf3-f0c77921d465" width="1390"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="781" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uplo